---
layout: main
---

<div class="intro">
  <div class="left-split">
    <img
      src="images/profpic.jpg"
      alt="avatar"
      class="avatar">
  </div>
  <div class="right-split">
    <h1>Hi, I'm JM 👋</h1>
    <p>I’m a
      <b>UX Designer</b>
      &
      <b>Researcher</b>
      with the goal of democratising new technologies straight from the oven 🍳</p>
    <p>As a
      <b>designer</b>
      &
      <b>developer</b>, I’m ready to put my skills to the test. I want to create new tools and help businesses improve. I value
      <b>innovation</b>
      and
      <b>growth</b>, always looking for opportunities to hone my skills as a
      <b>technologist</b>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="research">
  {% assign research = collections.research | sort: "years" %}
  {% for r in research limit: 3 %}
    <article>
      <img src="images/{{ r.data.image }}" alt="{{ r.data.imagealt }}">
      <div class="contents">
        <h1>{{ r.data.title }}</h1>
        <p>{{ r.data.excerpt }}</p>
      </div>
    </article>
  {% endfor %}
</div>